WEBVTT

00:00.260 --> 00:00.740
Hmm.

00:01.500 --> 00:04.970
The lab is full of critics, as usual.

00:06.200 --> 00:11.080
I passed the certification exam, yet everyone still treats me like I'm not good enough to be here.

00:11.980 --> 00:15.030
It's mostly Professor Takashima - he's awful.

00:16.190 --> 00:18.590
They refuse to give me any patients.

00:19.560 --> 00:21.940
Instead, they just dump all the menial jobs onto me.

00:23.520 --> 00:32.020
I bet he says to himself, "The girl studied abroad - she can't do anything properly.".  You're so annoying, Takeshi!

00:32.650 --> 00:34.890
Men get judged on their ability alone,

00:35.340 --> 00:38.590
but since I'm a woman, they think I'm useless because I studied overseas!

00:39.740 --> 00:42.790
It's not worth getting upset over Professor Takahashi's chores.

00:43.720 --> 00:45.630
I'll prove myself in time.
